WEBVTT

00:00:12.440 --> 00:00:13.240
Pham Hien

00:00:14.040 --> 00:00:16.340
I didn't expect you to be that kind of person.

00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:17.660
What kind of person am I?

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:19.260
Don't get me wrong.

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:22.340
His eyes have not moved since then.

00:00:23.280 --> 00:00:24.080
Pham Hien

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:25.660
I feel something is wrong.

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:27.020
Look at their faces.

00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:29.160
Happening is being urged.

00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:30.060
Go save people.

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:33.580
Stand up.

00:00:38.040 --> 00:00:40.460
Van Ha, what next?

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:42.360
let me think

00:00:42.360 --> 00:00:43.860
I will think of one for you.

00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:45.980
Just kill your wife.

00:00:46.480 --> 00:00:48.740
Killing is not my style.

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:50.320
Who are you?

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:57.280
The sect master of Ha Khong Khong Sect stole a knife and didn't know why the two of you barged into my sect.

00:00:57.280 --> 00:00:59.740
Stealing someone else's sect hall for yourself.

00:01:00.040 --> 00:01:01.240
He was very proud.

00:01:01.240 --> 00:01:02.500
I can steal.

00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:04.240
That is my ability.

00:01:04.240 --> 00:01:05.460
You come to steal, I will try.

00:01:05.800 --> 00:01:07.260
Children's material

00:01:09.120 --> 00:01:09.920
Yes.

00:01:10.280 --> 00:01:12.140
Grandpa, come listen.

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:16.300
Good boy, your little man is successful.

00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:21.340
Ha ha ha, this person has a lot of relationship with you, right?

00:01:21.560 --> 00:01:24.060
Let them live

00:01:24.440 --> 00:01:26.420
Come here and be my shadow.